  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK908">
<l>naṭṭār kuṟaimuṭiyār naṉṟāṟṟār naṉṉutalāḷ</l>
<l> peṭṭāṅ koḻuku pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who yield to the wishes of their wives will neither relieve the wants of (their) friends nor perform virtuous deeds.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
